OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774966279
OL,3,CDeal signed to turn Metrocentre into
OL,4,C'city within a city'
OL,6,FPlans to build 4,500 homes near the
OL,7,FMetrocentre in Gateshead have been
OL,8,Frevealed as part of an urban
OL,9,Fregeneration project aimed at creating
OL,10,Fa carbon-neutral "city within a city".
OL,12,FThe mixed-use development on the south
OL,13,Fbank of the River Tyne would be known
OL,14,Fas Metro Riverside.
OL,16,FThose behind it say it could create up
OL,17,Fto 5,000 jobs, house thousands of
OL,18,Fpeople and double the site's
OL,19,Fcontribution to the regional economy
OL,20,Fto more than #2 billion per annum by
OL,21,F2045.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
