OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774966279
OL,3,CDeal signed to turn Metrocentre into
OL,4,C'city within a city'
OL,6,FA deal has been signed by Metrocentre
OL,7,Fand Gateshead Council.
OL,9,FMartin Healy, chairman of Metrocentre,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Metro Riverside demonstrates
OL,11,Fthe power of long-term public-private
OL,12,Fpartnerships to unlock
OL,13,Ftransformational change. Developments
OL,14,Fof this scale and ambition simply
OL,15,Fcannot be delivered in isolation.
OL,26,@rD@GOU
