PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774966279
OL,3,CDeal signed to turn Metrocentre into
OL,4,C'city within a city'
OL,6,F"By working in partnership with
OL,7,FGateshead Council and others, we can
OL,8,Fbring together long term investment,
OL,9,Flocal leadership and shared purpose to
OL,10,Fcreate a new dense, urban community
OL,11,Fthat delivers homes, jobs and
OL,12,Fopportunities, while ensuring
OL,13,FMetrocentre continues to evolve as a
OL,14,Fmajor economic engine for the region
OL,15,Ffor decades to come."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@UO]
