PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774966279
OL,3,CDeal signed to turn Metrocentre into
OL,4,C'city within a city'
OL,6,FThe project would use brownfield land
OL,7,Faround the Metrocentre and would be
OL,8,Fdesigned as a "20-minute destination",
OL,9,Fwith the shopping and leisure complex
OL,10,Freimagined to serve the everyday needs
OL,11,Fof new residents and workers, while
OL,12,Fcontinuing to attract visitors from
OL,13,Facross the North East.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
